<p>
<h1>Who am I?</h1>
<p>
<div align=center>
I was born from the ultimate darkness, yet live in the purest light.<br>
I am wielder of swords; I am user of magic.<BR>
I am your worst nightmare; I am your greatest fantasy.<br>
A trusted friend, a hated enemy.<br>
A beacon of light, a wraith among shadows.<br>
I walk openly beside you, stalking your every move, waiting to pounce.<br>
I give you in one hand what I take from the other.<br>
</div>
<p>
<div align=center>
I am what you see when you look in the mirror.</div>
<p>
<div align=center>
I am thief, killer, friend, lover, companion, hunter, hero, villain.</div>
<p>
<div align=center>
I am one, I am all.</div>
<p>
<br>
<p>
<b><i><div align=center>I am Gleam.</div>
<p>
<div align=center>And I am here to take what is rightfully mine.</div></i></b>
